current_seasonId = value
	result = system.db.runNamedQuery("WinterShelter/Overview/GetTotalBeds_PerSeason",{'seasonId':current_seasonId})
	data = []
	if result.getRowCount()>0:
		for i in range(result.getRowCount()):
			seasonTitle = result.getValueAt(i,'seasonTitle')
			totalBeds = result.getValueAt(i,'TotalBeds')
			data.append({"x":seasonTitle,"y":totalBeds})
	
	return data
